sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant APP as Flutter App
  participant EDGE as ALB or API Gateway
  participant FOOD as Food Data Service
  participant RDS as RDS
  participant S3 as S3
  participant MAP as Google Maps
  participant EXT as Grab or FoodPanda

  U->>APP: Tap food card
  APP->>EDGE: GET food details
  EDGE->>FOOD: Fetch details
  FOOD->>RDS: Query food and restaurant info
  RDS-->>FOOD: Details and image keys
  FOOD-->>EDGE: Details
  EDGE-->>APP: Details

  APP->>S3: Load image
  S3-->>APP: Image
  APP-->>U: Show detail screen

  opt Order food
    U->>APP: Tap Order
    APP-->>EXT: Open external ordering app
  end

  opt Navigate to restaurant
    U->>APP: Tap Directions
    APP-->>MAP: Open navigation
  end
